<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Planets</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5ebe7;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: 800px;
            background-color: #1a1a3d;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            text-align: left;
        }

        .logo-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo-section img {
            width: 100px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .image-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .image-section img {
            width: 350px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .text-section {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            max-width: 750px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo-section">
            <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1252890/pexels-photo-1252890.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-krisof-1252890.jpg&fm=jpg" alt="Space Explorer Logo">
            <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/009/829/074/non_2x/astronaut-space-explorer-mascot-logo-vector.jpg" alt="Space Explorer Logo">
        </div>

        <h1>PLANETS</h1>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="image-section">
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Solar System">
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Planets Chart">
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Planet Sizes">
            </div>

            <div class="text-section">
                <p>
                    Planets are celestial bodies that orbit the Sun and have enough gravity to sustain their shape. 
                    They don’t produce their own light but reflect the Sun’s light.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
